<h1> <%= @garnish.name %> </h1>

<p> Edible: <%= if @garnish.edible; "Yes"; else; "No" end %> </p>

Cocktails that contain this garnish: 
<ul>
<% @garnish.cocktails.each do |cock| %> 
    <li> 
    <%= link_to "#{cock.name} by #{cock.user.name}", cocktail_path(cock) %>
    </li> 
<% end %> 
</ul>    

<h4>Click here for a random cocktail containing this garnish!<%= button_to "Show me the cocktail", @garnish, :method => :get %><br>
</h4>


<li>
<% cocktail = @garnish.cocktails.sample %> 
<%=link_to cocktail.name, cocktail_path(cocktail)%>
</li>